	Social activities and team-building events. 


In addition to the above benefits, we also have incentives for our sales teams such as competitions with incredible prizes! Challenge yourself, set your goals – smash those goals and you’ll see the rewards.

Over the last years, employees have enjoyed five nights in Las Vegas with a helicopter ride over the breath-taking Grand Canyon including a pit stop at the NHL awards; they partied in Nice with Jay-Z and Beyoncé, have taken in big English Premier League matches, Italy’s famous Roma and Milan derbies, and much more!

Keen to find out what’s coming up next? Get in touch today to discuss an opportunity to join our extraordinary team!We're the industry leaders in the retention & reactivation of churned players for some of the leading operators in the iGaming industry. We believe that hiring the best talent, with diversity in perspectives, ideas, and cultures, leads to the creation of better products and services for both our clients and their players.With our HQ in Malta, we are expanding with a new office in Bucharest (Romania) and we want you to join us in this adventure!/n

Personality:

	You are well organized, focused and able to meet strict deadlines ;
	Your mindset is based on improvement and growth ;
	You bring positive attitude ;
	You have passion in your blood.


Education:  


	Bachelor/Master’s degree in degree in Purchasing, Economics, Mechanical Engineering, Logistics


Experience and Skills:


	Broad knowledge of  procurement planning;
	3 years working experience in production environment, preferably automotive field ;
