Certifications: 


	MS-Office (Excel, Outlook, PowerPoint);
	SAP R/3 (MM, LE).


Languages:


	English – advanced level


Your valuable contribution to something big


	You are in charge of planning the customer orders in SAP;
	You are responsible of planning the amount and type of products to be produced;
	You are responsible of creating a leveling scheme;
	You ensure on-time delivery of products to BOSCH customers (right part, right amount, right time, right place -> according to customer wishes);
	You ensure availability of products and create delivery notes;
	You are responsible of customer contact management to coordinate demand;
	You ensure coordination with manufacturing and in-house production planner;
	You develop the production plan / leveling plan to ensure on-time delivery


#LikeABosch Benefits:


	25 days of annual leave, because work-life balance is essential to us; 
	Lunch discounts and daily subsidies at our canteen;
